text: Henry Gujer was a Swiss basketball player. He was one of those who competed in the men's tournament in the 1948 Summer Olympics. He was born on the 25th of April 1920 and died on the 4th of November 2017 at the age of 97. == References == Category:2017 deaths Category:1920 births Category:Olympians for Switzerland Category:Basketball players Category:Pages with unreviewed translations
title: Henry Gujer
